Fix: Remove the if block entirely. Also, for unnamed function statements (error case), it already returns early. So only function expressions with null name will reach here. So we can just not set line number.

Also, note that for named function expressions, isUnnamedFunction is false, so that block is not executed anyway. So it's safe to remove.

